data.description: Comfortable 4 bedroom 21/2 bathroom home in a great location in Lawrenceville.  Large driveway  and 2 car garage.  Flat Back yard.  Open concept main living area.  Formal dining room.  Large eat-in kitchen with stainless steel appliances.  New laminate and tile flooring throughout the home.  Secondary bedrooms are great in size.  Large master bedroom with seating area, 2 walk-in closets and on suite bathroom with separate tub and shower and double vanity.  Come and see it before it is gone.
